com.radiotelescope.contracts.log

Class AdminLogWrapper

  • com.radiotelescope.contracts.log.AdminLogWrapper

  • public class AdminLogWrapper

    Wrapper that takes a interface LogFactory and is responsible for all user role validations for endpoints for the Log Entity. NOTE: All endpoints require the user to be an admin.
